  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large Dutch oven over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the ground beef and cook until browned, breaking it up with a spoon as it cooks.",
    "Add the onion and cook until translucent.",
    "Sprinkle in caraway seeds and bonito flakes, stirring for 1 minute.",
    "Add the flour and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the beer and beef broth, stirring to combine.",
    "Bring to a simmer and cook for 10 minutes, or until the liquid has thickened slightly.",
    "Stir in milk and cook for an additional 5 minutes.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Sprinkle with parsley and serve hot, molten center and all."
